S.FORM: Si-ke-mung-de.fuo-luo-yi-de (kamu nu Hulam: 西格蒙德.佛洛伊德) nikaudip生平 yumahida早年 caywal-limnem mihcaan lima a bulad enem a demiad, pilacehan ni fuo-luo-yi-de itida i Aw-ti-li-ti-kuo-muo-la-wi-ya-Fuo-lay-paw a Yu-tay tademaw a lumaan, pilecuhan i Yu-tay a lumaan tu nikuda nipicudadan idaw ku satabakiay nu picuduhan. pilecuhan nina nida tulu ku tatamaan a wawaan atu lima ku tataynaan a wawaw, sakakaay nu tatamaan cinida, idaw hen ku caayay kalecad nu wamaan a wawaan. makelec ku nikaudip nu heni, adidi likecu ku luma', nika paicelan ku babalaki nu heni pahabay i tu nuhenian, micidek tu ci Fuo-luo-yi-dean. Nanuwawaw, micidek ku nipahabay tu tineng ci nidaan, tada micidek tu ku sapahabay ci nidaan mikikaka tu sapahabay tu calekakaan nida. 1856年5月6日, . pilecuhan nida idaw ku mikabitay tu pilanuan tu udip nida, saan cina nida u malemeday ku mahiniay sa, yu wawa henay cinida mikikakatu tu salal a tineng, saiwaay henay ku mihcaan tada kapah tu ku nicudadan mikiayaw tu salal micudadtu tu cun-sea, picudadan tu waluay a mihcaan pinanaman matulin cinida enemay a mihcaan u sayaway a ku nipicudadan, micidek ku sakay laylayan tu udipan u sayaway tu makaala tu pitu a mihcaan ku tenes nida a kapah. . itawya amica idaw ku mihantayay nu Yu-tay a masakaputay, nika cinida i caywal-piclu mihcaan micumud tu Wi-ye-na tabakiay a cacudadan minanam tu nu nabakuan a kawawan. picudadan henay tu tabakiay a nipicuda Fuo-luo-yi-de, manamuh cinida tu sakay cilekayan atu sakay udipan a kawawan, sipayayaw nidaku sapinanam tu sakay aadupan atu sakay udipan a minanam, yadahtu ku nihapuan nida tu nicudadan. tawya u mikinkiway tu namakabalucuay a sayda nida ci Fuo-lan-ce. Pu-lun-ta-nuo, kasikadan nida kina babalaki. caywal-walcay a mihcaan lima a bulad, ci Fuo-luo-yi-de malaheci tu nida ku sakay misaydan a nipihedek micudad , maala nida ku Puo-se a nipicudadan. . hedek satu micudad, ci Fuo-luo-yi-de mitulin itini i Nsete'-pulike' a pikingkiwan tu sakay udipan misakakawaw. atu ci Masa.puonayse nikuda nu nipikungyakuan, mangalay micunus tu kalisiw, miala cinida tu nakamuan ni Puli-ke' alesen nida ku sapikingkiwan tu lilun a cudadan, malamisaydan cinida. caywal-waltu mihcaan pitu a bulad lucay a demiad, ci Fuo-luo-yi-de malingatu i Wiyena'-cunhe padekuan mikuli, katukuh i caywal-wallin a mihcaan walu a bulad mala Wuy-ye-na tabakiay nu cacudadan a nu sinkicuan a saydan. 畢業後, . i tusip a mihcaan malalid mitabaku, saan mananam mitabaku taneng micuduh tu sakay kawawan sa. kaput nida ci Wi-lian.fuoli-se na tuduan tu ci nida, nika ci Fuo-luo-yi-de pakunida sa caay pitengil tu kamu nida, nikudan satu si imelang tu nu laway a nganang. anu hidan u nakamuan ni Fuo-luo-yi-de tu caywal-siwpic a mihcaan atu ci Fuo-li-se, malalid nu pitabakuan mahida u nipisulasulay sa. 他在24 . alesan nida ku sakasikadan a saydangan ci Fuo-lan-ce. Pu-lun-ta-nuo, kanamuhan nida ci Siaw-duo.Lipu-se atu ci Ni-cay a nisanga'an. nikapatayan ni Ni-cay tu caysiw-sepsep a mihcaan, ci Fuo-luo-yi-de u ni Ni-cay sa ku cakayen tu nisanga'an nida tu kawaw. nika i nikuda caay tu ka namuh tu kawaw ni Ni-cay, malingatu tu micudad tu sakay sinki a cudadan, namahida hina cudad cinida tu inggu nu cudadan ni Sase-piya, nikahida yadah ku namaka ci Sase-piya a cudadan ku yadahay nu nikiliman tu tatapangan nu sakay udipan a sapikinkiwan tu cudadan. . Kasinganganan 成名 Caywal-walpic a nipikulitan tu Zeang-Matin.sake pisakamuan tu cudadan a waywayan, ci Fuo-luo-yi-de i pikawawan nida a kitidaan idaw ku nipiinsacuan nida tu Wiyena'- Fuo-luo-yi-de a nalumaan, aydaay nu Fuo-luo-yi-de puow-kuen. 30 537 Caywal-wallin a mihcaan caysep a bulad ci Fuo-luo-yi-de tayda i Pa-li pasayda ci Zeang-Matin.sake paayaawi kaku sa, sakamusa cinida tina kawawan, saan namaka udip tu pasaydan i nu sinkicuan mikinkiw idaw ku nikinkiwan tu kawawan sa. saka tusa a mihcaan sacacay satu ci nida mikinkiw, tawya pikinkiwan ni Fuo-luo-yi-de tada ba'ket tu, hina sepi, nika hinian nida namaka wamaan nida tu cawal- siwnem a mihcaan nikapatayan ni ama nida sisa hida satu malawacu. nai tawyaay tu a nikinkiwan, ci Fuo-luo-yi-de micuduh tu tademaw nu wawaan tu nisawacuan, tu nikudan satu mala nipacician tunusinkican atu kalaapaapaan a kawawan, u Fuo-luo-yi-de sapiala tu balucu han a cudadan. 1885年10月, . caywal-walnem mihcaan, siacawa cinida ci Masa.-Puonay-se, a enem ku wawa nu heni. tuyniyan a mihcaan miales cinida tu sakay misaydan, i Wi-ye-na misiwbay tu padekuan. 1886年, . malaalitin tu i hekalay atu zumaay a natinengan

Si-ke-mong-de.foo-loo-yi-de (kamo no Holam: 西格蒙德.佛洛伊德) nikaodip生平 yomahida早年 caywal-limnem mihcaan lima a bolad enem a demiad, pilacehan ni foo-loo-yi-de itida i Aw-ti-li-ti-koo-moo-la-wi-ya-Foo-lay-paw a Yo-tay tademaw a lomaan, pilecohan i Yo-tay a lomaan to nikoda nipicodadan idaw ko satabakiay no picodohan. pilecohan nina nida tolo ko tatamaan a wawaan ato lima ko tataynaan a wawaw, sakakaay no tatamaan cinida, idaw hen ko caayay kalecad no wamaan a wawaan. makelec ko nikaodip no heni, adidi likeco ko loma', nika paicelan ko babalaki no heni pahabay i to nohenian, micidek to ci Foo-loo-yi-dean. Nanowawaw, micidek ko nipahabay to tineng ci nidaan, tada micidek to ko sapahabay ci nidaan mikikaka to sapahabay to calekakaan nida. 1856年5月6日, . pilecohan nida idaw ko mikabitay to pilanoan to odip nida, saan cina nida o malemeday ko mahiniay sa, yo wawa henay cinida mikikakato to salal a tineng, saiwaay henay ko mihcaan tada kapah to ko nicodadan mikiayaw to salal micodadto to con-sea, picodadan to waloay a mihcaan pinanaman matolin cinida enemay a mihcaan o sayaway a ko nipicodadan, micidek ko sakay laylayan to odipan o sayaway to makaala to pito a mihcaan ko tenes nida a kapah. . itawya amica idaw ko mihantayay no Yo-tay a masakapotay, nika cinida i caywal-piclo mihcaan micomod to Wi-ye-na tabakiay a cacodadan minanam to no nabakoan a kawawan. picodadan henay to tabakiay a nipicoda Foo-loo-yi-de, manamoh cinida to sakay cilekayan ato sakay odipan a kawawan, sipayayaw nidako sapinanam to sakay aadopan ato sakay odipan a minanam, yadahto ko nihapoan nida to nicodadan. tawya o mikinkiway to namakabalocoay a sayda nida ci Foo-lan-ce. Po-lon-ta-noo, kasikadan nida kina babalaki. caywal-walcay a mihcaan lima a bolad, ci Foo-loo-yi-de malaheci to nida ko sakay misaydan a nipihedek micodad , maala nida ko Poo-se a nipicodadan. . hedek sato micodad, ci Foo-loo-yi-de mitolin itini i Nsete'-polike' a pikingkiwan to sakay odipan misakakawaw. ato ci Masa.poonayse nikoda no nipikongyakoan, mangalay miconos to kalisiw, miala cinida to nakamoan ni Poli-ke' alesen nida ko sapikingkiwan to lilon a codadan, malamisaydan cinida. caywal-walto mihcaan pito a bolad locay a demiad, ci Foo-loo-yi-de malingato i Wiyena'-conhe padekoan mikoli, katokoh i caywal-wallin a mihcaan walo a bolad mala Woy-ye-na tabakiay no cacodadan a no sinkicoan a saydan. 畢業後, . i tosip a mihcaan malalid mitabako, saan mananam mitabako taneng micodoh to sakay kawawan sa. kapot nida ci Wi-lian.fooli-se na todoan to ci nida, nika ci Foo-loo-yi-de pakonida sa caay pitengil to kamo nida, nikodan sato si imelang to no laway a nganang. ano hidan o nakamoan ni Foo-loo-yi-de to caywal-siwpic a mihcaan ato ci Foo-li-se, malalid no pitabakoan mahida o nipisolasolay sa. 他在24 . alesan nida ko sakasikadan a saydangan ci Foo-lan-ce. Po-lon-ta-noo, kanamohan nida ci Siaw-doo.Lipo-se ato ci Ni-cay a nisanga'an. nikapatayan ni Ni-cay to caysiw-sepsep a mihcaan, ci Foo-loo-yi-de o ni Ni-cay sa ko cakayen to nisanga'an nida to kawaw. nika i nikoda caay to ka namoh to kawaw ni Ni-cay, malingato to micodad to sakay sinki a codadan, namahida hina codad cinida to inggo no codadan ni Sase-piya, nikahida yadah ko namaka ci Sase-piya a codadan ko yadahay no nikiliman to tatapangan no sakay odipan a sapikinkiwan to codadan. . Kasinganganan 成名 Caywal-walpic a nipikolitan to Zeang-Matin.sake pisakamoan to codadan a waywayan, ci Foo-loo-yi-de i pikawawan nida a kitidaan idaw ko nipiinsacoan nida to Wiyena'- Foo-loo-yi-de a nalomaan, aydaay no Foo-loo-yi-de poow-koen. 30 537 Caywal-wallin a mihcaan caysep a bolad ci Foo-loo-yi-de tayda i Pa-li pasayda ci Zeang-Matin.sake paayaawi kako sa, sakamosa cinida tina kawawan, saan namaka odip to pasaydan i no sinkicoan mikinkiw idaw ko nikinkiwan to kawawan sa. saka tosa a mihcaan sacacay sato ci nida mikinkiw, tawya pikinkiwan ni Foo-loo-yi-de tada ba'ket to, hina sepi, nika hinian nida namaka wamaan nida to cawal- siwnem a mihcaan nikapatayan ni ama nida sisa hida sato malawaco. nai tawyaay to a nikinkiwan, ci Foo-loo-yi-de micodoh to tademaw no wawaan to nisawacoan, to nikodan sato mala nipacician tonosinkican ato kalaapaapaan a kawawan, o Foo-loo-yi-de sapiala to baloco han a codadan. 1885年10月, . caywal-walnem mihcaan, siacawa cinida ci Masa.-Poonay-se, a enem ko wawa no heni. toyniyan a mihcaan miales cinida to sakay misaydan, i Wi-ye-na misiwbay to padekoan. 1886年, . malaalitin to i hekalay ato zomaay a natinengan
